# Description
Generates super simple TOC (Table of Content) for git MD files. 

# Installation
```
$ git clone <repo>
```

```
$ cd git-toc
$ python setup.py install
```

# Usage
Below command will print TOC which you can embed to e.g. ```README.md```.
```
$ gittoc -f <file>
```

## Example
```
$ gittoc.exe -f TESTING.md
```
